data.description: Welcome home to your piece of paradise in this all-age gated community in Coconut Creek. Nestled in the serene development of CocoBay, this home backs up to a private preserve with beautiful trees that provides peace and quiet. Renovated Kitchen, Vaulted ceilings, neutral tile and wood laminate flooring throughout.  Master bedroom boasts enough room for a sitting area.  Minutes from the Coconut Creek Promenade that offers some of the best restaurants, movie theaters and retail shops! Really does show bright and welcoming! Don't miss this chance to call this your home! Low HOA fees of only $168 per month. VA loan assumable at only 2.25% for those who qualify.
